node.text:
➡️Follow @steez for more ‼️
French designer #ThierryGaugain has revealed his concept for the $350M “G-Train”‼️🔥 The 1,300 foot private train is made up of 14 different cars that feature a state-of-the-art glass exterior that changes colors and transparency based on the environment the train is in. The train also comes with 20 guest rooms, a gym, and a spa. How’s it looking⁉️
